  <!-- TempData success / error messages set by CitizenController.
       Surface in the alert-success / alert-danger banners on the
       citizen Create and Details views. Forwarded ValidationException
       / DomainException messages (ex.Message) are NOT localised by
       this commit — they come from the domain layer's exception
       payloads and need separate work in the Application layer. -->
